rtlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9dq","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3375,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/12\/recite-quran-too-fast\/","url_meta":{"origin":35428,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Recitation: Quran should not be recited too quickly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne has not understood the Quran if he reads it in less than three days.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2949 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0647\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38653,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/01\/26\/taleem-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":35428,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Teaching: Best Muslims teach Quran they have learned","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 26, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of you are those who learn the Quran and teach it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0